  "texts": [
    "This model is designed to address the limitations of max pooling and average pooling.",
    "CNN is widely used in computer vision applications.",
    "Its main function in these applications is to automatically extract image features.",
    "In the convolutional layers of CNN, the input values undergo filtering operations to extract the features of the image.",
    "Through these filtering operations, CNN can identify unique features within the image."
  ]
}